title: FUBAR Disk Stresser 2014
description:
FUBAR Disk Stresser 2014
------------------------

A new version in this evil series of applications!

This application will put your harddisks (and Windows) under a lot of stress, reducing performance significantly.


When you run this application, it will give you 1 (ONE!) warning, asking you if you really want to run it.
If you click on 'Yes', several threads will be launched, each one reading from random files on your harddisks.

After some time, maybe a couple of hours, all the threads will end.


Nothing is installed!



/Ubehage
